@node requirements
@title "Requirements"

 For  this  cardset  -  due  to  its colour-depth (24bit) - a graphic board with
 CyberGraphX  is recommended (eg.  CyberVision64/3D, Picasso II, Retina, Piccolo
 etc.).

 Due  to  the  size  of  cards  also  a screen resolution of 800 x 600 is highly
 recommended  ...    in  other  words ...  i don't even know wether or not it is
 possible to play this cardset on a smaller screen (...  to lazy to test ...).

 I recommend a registered version of CyberGraphX since the unregistered  version
 doesn't support 24 bit screenmodes.

@endnode

