@node history
@title "History"


 @{bold "February 1995"}
 
 Initial release for Klondike Deluxe AGA (III) by REKO Productions.

 @{bold "1996"}
 
 Internal  conversion  for CyberPatience.  Never released.  CyberPatience seemed
 to  be  a  day  fly.  And so it was ...  sad but true.  No known version higher
 than v1.02.

 @{bold "March 1997"}
 
 Converted  to  the  'Soliton' cardset format, which luckily doesn't differ that
 much  to  the  Klondike  cardset  format (...  thanks Kai ...  it took about 10
 minutes).

@endnode

